Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.16,0:00:02.62,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, let's get crackin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.62,0:00:03.56,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's-a-go.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.23,0:00:06.02,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop messing around and start!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.29,0:01:31.88,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,'Kay!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.88,0:01:33.55,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, have a seat!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.84,0:01:35.88,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Happy New Year.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.38,0:01:38.22,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The year just flew by, didn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.22,0:01:39.62,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's have another good'un.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.93,0:01:40.89,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,'Course...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.18,0:01:45.02,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...I'll be biddin' farewell to some of y'all in three more months.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.02,0:01:46.35,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Guess who I'm talkin' about.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.35,0:01:46.98,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Teacher!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.98,0:01:48.35,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't mean me, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.35,0:01:49.85,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I can believe, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.96,0:01:50.96,ls_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(455,229)}Savory\NDay
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.52,0:01:54.19,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,People always talk about the New Year's mood...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.19,0:01:56.61,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...but I guess there's kinda a weird atmosphere.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.61,0:01:59.70,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But it changes the second school starts.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.70,0:02:01.37,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Unfortunately...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.37,0:02:02.20,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.20,0:02:05.58,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true that New Year's wields a mysterious power.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.58,0:02:09.50,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Despite the fact that I spent the first three\Ndays of the year busy working at home...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.83,0:02:11.63,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...I gained weight!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.63,0:02:12.96,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}New Year's magic, huh?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.84,0:02:16.67,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The cold weather makes it difficult to burn off your fat.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.67,0:02:18.26,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I did a lot of moving around though.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.26,0:02:20.47,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Three days of busy work as a shrine maiden.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.72,0:02:22.05,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But you ate just as much, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.30,0:02:23.01,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Shrine maiden. New Year's food!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.01,0:02:23.72,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Shrine maiden. Zoni soup!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.72,0:02:24.35,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Shrine maiden. Snacks!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.35,0:02:25.47,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Snacks! Snacks! Snacks!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.47,0:02:26.18,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Shrine maiden. Snacks!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.18,0:02:27.22,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.27,0:02:30.77,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But the pictures of having fun during New Year's...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.06,0:02:31.85,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...usually include badminton...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.86,0:02:32.90,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...One Hundred Poets...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.90,0:02:34.98,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...and kite flying...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.98,0:02:37.90,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...but I've never actually seen someone do those.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.90,0:02:38.61,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.61,0:02:42.32,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,These days, it's dangerous with stuff like electric lines and cars.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.32,0:02:45.16,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I just watched TV and read books.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.16,0:02:46.99,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,After those first three busy days.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.33,0:02:48.16,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.16,0:02:49.96,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I did those.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.96,0:02:53.50,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I enjoyed badminton, One Hundred\NPoets, and Pin the Tail on the Donkey.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.04,0:02:55.17,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't match your image.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.59,0:02:57.71,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,My family follows western customs...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.71,0:03:00.13,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...but our relatives in the country are more traditional.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.68,0:03:03.34,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We wore kimonos and went to the temple on New Year's...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.35,0:03:05.83,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...and I had fun with my cousins.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.83,0:03:07.70,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}An omnipotent god...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.48,0:03:10.27,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Way more Japanese than I am!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.27,0:03:11.39,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}More traditional than my family!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.39,0:03:12.98,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Wait, why Pin the Tail on the Donkey?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.42,0:03:14.86,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,In One Hundred Poets...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.86,0:03:17.02,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...they're all 31 syllable poems, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.28,0:03:17.82,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.82,0:03:19.23,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You read out the first verse...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.24,0:03:21.74,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...and look for the card with the rest of the poem.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.74,0:03:22.99,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You must have skills...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.20,0:03:23.95,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.95,0:03:25.53,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just a beginner.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.53,0:03:28.74,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The expert snatch up the cards in a flash.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.75,0:03:30.25,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, more like...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.25,0:03:34.17,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't stand playing a game that\Nmakes you feel like you're studying.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.17,0:03:37.84,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,People like you who view mental games as a\Nchore are why Japan's going down the drain.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.21,0:03:41.47,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Why couldn't they use One Hundred Poets for like a card battle?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.47,0:03:42.66,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You could summon a monk.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.66,0:03:44.39,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Think there was a Semimaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.39,0:03:46.39,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Semimaru uses a shining attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.39,0:03:48.43,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Ono no Komachi uses a lovely strike!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.72,0:03:49.93,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't that sound fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.93,0:03:50.93,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Back to your world, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.18,0:03:55.52,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But wouldn't more physical games have helped you lose weight?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.52,0:03:56.36,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Be quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.73,0:03:58.32,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It was those stupid rice cakes...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.32,0:04:00.90,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Rice cakes are loaded with calories, aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.90,0:04:02.65,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,One as big as a matchbox...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.65,0:04:05.57,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...is equivalent to a whole bowl of rice.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.57,0:04:08.20,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Which means that Kagami's eating a bowl of rice with each bite?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.20,0:04:08.58,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.58,0:04:10.16,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You also ate rice cakes, didn't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.83,0:04:15.00,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,My mom's gone, so I've rarely had zoni soup and that stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.14,0:04:15.00,ls_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}[zoni soup: a broth eaten with rice cakes; New Year's meal]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.46,0:04:17.54,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, I don't really eat rice cakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.88,0:04:18.88,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a waste.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.25,0:04:21.59,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,With zoni soup, sweet red bean soup, soy flour rice cakes...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.59,0:04:23.76,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,There are so many fun ways to eat them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.51,0:04:27.51,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like she's gonna lose to the rice cakes again next year...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.51,0:04:28.14,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...Kagami.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.06,0:04:32.47,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you have to eat for New Year's...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.48,0:04:34.64,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...instead of rice cakes, Izumi-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.64,0:04:36.10,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Stuff like pizza and pasta.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.81,0:04:39.98,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Our year starts with raw pasta.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.98,0:04:43.86,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,My dad cleans out the pasta machine at the end of every year.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.86,0:04:44.74,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.74,0:04:47.82,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That thing rusts if you don't use it for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.82,0:04:49.74,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,If you use it without cleaning it first...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.74,0:04:52.24,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...the pasta ends up all black and stuff...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.25,0:04:54.12,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So we clean it out...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.12,0:04:57.04,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...and make pasta and pizza!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.04,0:04:58.63,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds very thorough.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.63,0:05:02.59,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, Kagami's house probably orders\Npizza and their pasta consists of cup noodles.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.05,0:05:05.09,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,More like...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.09,0:05:07.30,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have pizza or pasta on New Year's...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.51,0:05:07.97,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.47,0:05:10.35,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't go with traditional foods.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.33,0:05:11.10,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure it does!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.10,0:05:13.31,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It goes great with roast chicken!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.31,0:05:14.35,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a traditional New Year's food?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.75,0:05:15.85,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.85,0:05:17.64,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Under western traditions.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.15,0:05:19.40,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's how it works?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.81,0:05:22.86,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you have for New Year's, Miyuki-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.86,0:05:23.90,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.24,0:05:27.82,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Your family sounds all wealthy and western...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.82,0:05:30.49,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...so you probably didn't have traditional stuff or rice cakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.49,0:05:32.87,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe you had like a full course French dinner!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.24,0:05:35.00,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.75,0:05:37.50,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I ate traditional foods...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.50,0:05:39.38,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...and I was unable to bite through a rice cake...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.38,0:05:41.71,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...and it stretched like whee!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.21,0:05:45.13,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What's with this walking pillar to elements of turn-ons?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.13,0:05:46.51,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Rice cake goes whee!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.97,0:05:50.01,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But New Year's goes by so fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.01,0:05:51.01,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.01,0:05:52.89,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Winter break goes by fast, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.89,0:05:54.97,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's supposed to be a long vacation...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.97,0:05:57.81,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...but after cleaning, writing New Year's cards, and homework...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.81,0:05:59.98,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...you don't have much time to relax, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.06,0:06:01.02,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.02,0:06:02.27,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't do New Year's cards this year!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.27,0:06:03.65,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And you copied my homework yesterday!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.73,0:06:05.40,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.40,0:06:07.57,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you have your first dream of the year, Kona-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.20,0:06:11.07,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it supposed to be a good\Nomen if you dream about certain things?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.07,0:06:12.07,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep, yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.08,0:06:16.54,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Usually, it's one: Mt. Fuji, two: hawk, three: eggplant.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.54,0:06:18.29,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Officially, you would add...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.29,0:06:22.58,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...four: fan, five: tobacco, six: blind man.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.34,0:06:25.46,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It goes all the way up to six!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.46,0:06:26.05,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.30,0:06:29.17,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Who ever dreams about that kind of stuff?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.18,0:06:29.93,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of dream would that be?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.93,0:06:31.30,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And why a blind man?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.30,0:06:32.01,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Pretty much...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.39,0:06:33.14,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.14,0:06:35.43,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have to dream about all of those at once?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.43,0:06:38.52,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,If all of those showed up in your dreams, you'd be really blessed...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.52,0:06:40.89,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...but I believe that just one will suffice.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.27,0:06:45.61,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you would have to dream about\Na hawk twice and an eggplant three times.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.90,0:06:47.34,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And quite frankly...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.36,0:06:50.57,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Who really remembers what they dream about?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.57,0:06:54.12,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,People who care about that stuff are\Nhaving way too much fun with New Year's.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.12,0:06:54.70,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You have a point.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.12,0:06:56.83,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,In my first dream this year...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.83,0:07:00.29,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...I opened my shoe locker to find my shoes missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.29,0:07:04.08,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So I had no choice but to take\Nshoes from someone else's open locker...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.09,0:07:06.84,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...but the size was wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.55,0:07:11.18,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I looked up the meaning of this dream in\Nthe encyclopedia for dream fortune telling...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.18,0:07:13.76,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...and it said that it's a sign I am pursuing skills useful to society...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.76,0:07:18.89,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...but it will take a while before I accomplish that goal.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.89,0:07:23.15,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The shoes apparently represent societal standing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.15,0:07:24.44,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Cheesecake?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.44,0:07:25.65,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Miyuki-san's...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.65,0:07:27.15,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...pretty ambitious.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.15,0:07:29.03,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like I kinda understand, but kinda not...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.82,0:07:36.45,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Another person was goofing off on the stage...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.45,0:07:38.70,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...during the coming-of-age ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.70,0:07:41.87,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't they realize they're representing Japan?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.87,0:07:44.63,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Makes you wonder why they even bother going.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.63,0:07:45.54,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,No kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.92,0:07:49.67,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't want to go to a boring coming-of-age ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.67,0:07:52.34,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And this girl's gonna grow up to be a bad person.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.72,0:07:56.39,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you guys going to wear to your ceremony?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.39,0:07:59.39,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Might as well go with a long-sleeve kimono...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.93,0:08:01.56,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.56,0:08:02.43,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.44,0:08:05.60,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,My dad's probably going to have me wear a long-sleeve kimono.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.06,0:08:06.98,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I can see him doing that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.38,0:08:08.38,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Yahoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.92,0:08:08.38,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.82,0:08:10.11,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,When you wear one...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.11,0:08:12.24,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...you'd look more like a little kid going to the festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.24,0:08:14.03,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Happy New Year!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.03,0:08:14.91,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hope ya had fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.91,0:08:17.24,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Happy New Year, Cousin Yui.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.24,0:08:18.58,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't seen you in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.58,0:08:20.16,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, my husband was here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.16,0:08:21.66,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And a lot happens during New Year's.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.66,0:08:24.21,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, and my sister had a fever.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.21,0:08:26.04,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,She's got a weak body.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.04,0:08:26.92,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.92,0:08:29.50,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It definitely wasn't because I didn't\Ngive her any New Year's allowance!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.50,0:08:31.09,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get the wrong idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.09,0:08:34.17,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Only a cop would reveal what she was\Nreally thinking before I've said a thing.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.38,0:08:36.59,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,A One Hundred Poets tournament is currently underway...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.59,0:08:38.55,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...and it's been one crazy ride so far.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.56,0:08:39.64,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.02,0:08:44.31,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you do on New Year's when you were a kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.31,0:08:45.64,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,When I was a kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.06,0:08:49.02,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I did all kinds of stuff...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.02,0:08:49.90,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.90,0:08:51.61,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.11,0:08:55.43,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Dot.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.68,0:08:56.01,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Dot.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.26,0:08:56.59,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Dot.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.84,0:08:56.97,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Dot.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.20,0:08:57.61,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.62,0:08:58.24,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I forgot.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.24,0:08:59.66,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,No clue.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.66,0:09:02.12,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She really just goes with the flow.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.12,0:09:04.46,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I've never heard her say anything serious.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.46,0:09:06.17,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Guess I outgrew my memories!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.59,0:09:14.26,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsukasa's always cooped up under the kotatsu these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.26,0:09:15.72,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,'Cause it's cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.18,0:09:17.26,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I know what you mean!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.26,0:09:18.55,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Kotatsus are so wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.55,0:09:21.51,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Going to the bathroom's a pain though.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.51,0:09:22.47,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep, yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.97,0:09:25.02,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But you shouldn't say that so loudly...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.02,0:09:28.69,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But we have a surefire way to get a person out of a kotatsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.31,0:09:30.06,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,How does it work?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.61,0:09:31.36,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Konata.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.36,0:09:33.11,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,If you stay under the kotatsu too long...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.11,0:09:34.53,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...you'll get stuck.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.03,0:09:37.28,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So your dad doesn't need a kotatsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.28,0:09:38.95,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,He likes them as much as the next person.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.95,0:09:40.28,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just like a warning.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.58,0:09:43.74,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,'Cause we've both fallen asleep together under the kotatsu before.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.25,0:09:45.45,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I know what you mean!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.46,0:09:48.08,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But they say that you'll catch a\Ncold if you fall asleep under a kotatsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.08,0:09:48.71,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.71,0:09:51.54,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So we turn it off once someone notices.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.54,0:09:55.05,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like a mix of heaven and hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.92,0:09:58.05,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Like right before you turn it on...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.05,0:10:01.30,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...and after you turn it off, it feels even colder.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.01,0:10:03.97,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I totally know what you mean!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.97,0:10:06.31,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And doesn't it really suck when you get out of bed in the morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.98,0:10:11.15,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,While we're at it, it's totally freezing after you\Nget undressed and before you get in the bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.15,0:10:13.94,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But not enough to make you run.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.94,0:10:15.15,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You might slip and fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.44,0:10:18.65,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And doesn't it suck when you need to go\Nthe bathroom in the middle of the night?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.32,0:10:20.07,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I hate that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.41,0:10:21.03,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.03,0:10:21.99,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,This is our stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.99,0:10:25.24,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And the trip from the bus to the classroom is also hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.62,0:10:28.33,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's almost Valentine's Day.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.58,0:10:31.17,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It always gets a lot more exciting this time of year.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.17,0:10:36.71,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It kinda tickles me how everyone can get so worked up every year.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.09,0:10:39.76,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Having someone special on this day...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.76,0:10:41.14,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...and confessing your feelings...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.14,0:10:42.34,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...and having them reciprocated...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.35,0:10:44.01,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...is a beautiful thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.72,0:10:47.52,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You're such a girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.52,0:10:50.52,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I just see it as a conspiracy by the chocolate industry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.15,0:10:54.48,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I guess you could say it's also a special time of year for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.98,0:10:57.78,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,They have a sale on the unsold chocolate afterwards...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.78,0:11:00.03,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...so I'm looking for chocolate to use in making my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.03,0:11:02.20,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And you, you have no dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.37,0:11:04.37,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Money can't buy love!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.37,0:11:05.37,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,At least, that's what they like to say...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.37,0:11:08.95,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...but isn't Valentine chocolate a\Nway of showing love through money?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.96,0:11:12.42,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess someone who's only\Nexperienced love in games has some harsh views.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.71,0:11:18.17,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, in games, it's all about upping\Nyour relationship level before the day comes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.34,0:11:22.89,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't do anything special for Valentine's.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.89,0:11:23.97,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Guys dream too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.30,0:11:27.10,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody managed to trigger the Kagami flag.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.10,0:11:28.68,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.33,0:11:30.68,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm super popular!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.69,0:11:31.35,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.35,0:11:32.77,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,In your game.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.77,0:11:36.02,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,When you talk about flags and relationship levels...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.02,0:11:37.90,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...I seriously get worried about your future.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.90,0:11:40.36,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't limit yourself to events in games.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.53,0:11:44.78,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't stand those narrow-minded people\Nwho don't know what they're talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.45,0:11:46.64,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So I'm wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.66,0:11:50.00,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Lately, events only take a few hours in game time...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.00,0:11:52.67,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...so Valentine's Day is usually over in a flash.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.67,0:11:53.50,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So what?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.88,0:11:57.34,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But this year, I'm planning on giving chocolate to someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.96,0:11:58.71,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.55,0:12:01.67,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone playing the same online game as me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.22,0:12:03.22,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,A friend from your game?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.80,0:12:04.93,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You're giving it to him in person?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.47,0:12:08.93,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not actually going to meet the person.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.89,0:12:12.39,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be in-game.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.39,0:12:14.35,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Since the characters are still human.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.35,0:12:15.94,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Does that even count?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.40,0:12:18.48,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So you just meant a game character.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.48,0:12:20.15,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you insult my bride!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.82,0:12:21.32,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Bride?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.90,0:12:25.11,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We're married in-game, and my character's male.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.12,0:12:25.66,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.87,0:12:26.82,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a sec.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.83,0:12:28.78,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So the guy is giving the girl chocolate?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.79,0:12:31.45,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And wouldn't it be like a girl giving a girl chocolate?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.45,0:12:33.04,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,If the other person's a girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.04,0:12:33.96,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.96,0:12:35.71,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The other person's a guy in real life.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.84,0:12:41.42,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Guess it doesn't matter as long as you're having fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.42,0:12:42.61,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Got that right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.84,0:12:44.76,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna go overseas.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.76,0:12:46.84,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That came out of nowhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.85,0:12:49.14,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, yesterday, Miyuki-san was like...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.14,0:12:54.31,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Females giving chocolates on February 14th is a Japanese custom.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.83,0:12:53.29,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}Miyuki-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.31,0:12:56.27,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,In western society, people of both genders...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.27,0:12:59.98,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...give chocolate and cards to friends and people they like.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.65,0:13:02.69,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what she said...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.69,0:13:05.99,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...so a girl like me could still get lots of chocolate!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.99,0:13:07.57,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess you could interpret it that way...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.57,0:13:09.28,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...but you sure have a lot of confidence in yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.28,0:13:10.95,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Like you already know for a fact that you'll be popular.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.95,0:13:12.70,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.70,0:13:13.91,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,In foreign countries, little girls...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.91,0:13:14.83,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.83,0:13:16.79,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,No risqué statements allowed!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.42,0:13:18.29,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.29,0:13:18.88,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you accept this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.21,0:13:20.79,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Happy Valentine's Day!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.80,0:13:22.42,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, Kona-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.80,0:13:25.01,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Incredible wrapping...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.01,0:13:25.67,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...for a uniform...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.97,0:13:28.39,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And the inside's all cool and heart-shaped!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.45,0:13:30.89,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I put some effort into it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.89,0:13:33.31,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsukasa's always enthusiastic about this kind of stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.31,0:13:35.85,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,She was making them until morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.85,0:13:37.39,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And it's only friendship chocolate.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.65,0:13:38.52,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsukasa.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.52,0:13:40.90,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't give any friendship chocolate to guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.90,0:13:42.61,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,They'll definitely get the wrong idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.94,0:13:43.44,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.49,0:13:46.24,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.24,0:13:48.53,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Kagami's giving me chocolate!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.53,0:13:49.74,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsukasa was making hers...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.74,0:13:50.99,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...so I just joined in.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.99,0:13:51.58,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't want it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.12,0:13:59.71,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Kagami looking like she's good at everything when\Nshe actually sucks so she secretly works hard turns me on.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.98,0:13:59.69,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}Zip it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.71,0:14:00.75,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up and put it away.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.17,0:14:03.25,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.25,0:14:04.17,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Kagami?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.22,0:14:09.01,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.01,0:14:10.30,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,This is for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.30,0:14:11.72,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Just so you know, it's a just friends thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.72,0:14:12.76,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Friendship chocolate.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.52,0:14:15.97,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sorry the shape's funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.98,0:14:17.50,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Silly.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.52,0:14:18.73,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The shape isn't important.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.73,0:14:21.48,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What matters is that you made it for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.11,0:14:23.40,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.40,0:14:25.40,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you it's not like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.61,0:14:26.94,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.95,0:14:27.61,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.61,0:14:28.78,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Just shut up and put it away.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.95,0:14:30.11,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,This is my first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.12,0:14:31.16,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The first time's most important.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.53,0:14:33.70,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So did you give anybody chocolate, Miyuki-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.04,0:14:36.91,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I gave chocolate to my father and a relative.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.12,0:14:40.25,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I gave chocolate to everybody I'm friendly with.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.50,0:14:42.50,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I gave chocolate to you, Tsukasa, and Miyuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.75,0:14:43.67,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.67,0:14:45.88,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys sure had a boring St. Valentine's Day.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.88,0:14:48.22,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't need to hear it from someone who lives in an online game.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.05,0:14:51.05,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.05,0:14:53.18,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Your cousin was accepted to Ryouou, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.68,0:14:54.56,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,She was.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.56,0:14:56.43,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's pretty far from her home...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.43,0:14:58.39,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...so she'll be living with us starting next month.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.39,0:15:00.56,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,She's always been like a little sister anyway...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.56,0:15:02.15,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...so we've been in touch.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.15,0:15:02.60,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Really.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.00,0:15:04.36,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But next to you...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.36,0:15:06.32,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...nobody would be able to tell who's younger.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.69,0:15:07.48,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,No, like I said...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.49,0:15:10.15,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,She's like a little sister in more ways than one.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.16,0:15:11.32,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She's that small?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.68,0:15:13.55,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But if she got accepted to our school...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.55,0:15:15.49,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...your cousin must be really smart.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.49,0:15:18.20,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That just sounds like you're being really presumptuous.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.20,0:15:19.04,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Since you're a student here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.29,0:15:22.00,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But I barely passed the exam.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.50,0:15:23.67,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Exams, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.67,0:15:26.09,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be taking our exams next year.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.84,0:15:28.51,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Guess I'll be spending the whole year studying.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.97,0:15:29.92,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds awful.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.92,0:15:30.67,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Exams...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.68,0:15:31.68,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Should I even take them?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.68,0:15:33.64,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't even picked a major.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.64,0:15:35.76,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You seriously need to start thinking about your future.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.02,0:15:40.81,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Studying, manual labor, and me just don't mix.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.81,0:15:43.44,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of future do you have in mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.79,0:15:46.50,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\i1}I design games. 'Cause it's my hobby.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.17,0:15:49.55,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\i1}Megas smoked cheese-nyoro.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.01,0:15:51.80,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\i1}There can only be one truth!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.80,0:15:52.72,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\i1}And this isn't it!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.65,0:15:46.57,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Use a hobby to make profit and make games...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.57,0:15:49.61,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Be a self-proclaimed manga artist who can only sell at Comiket...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.61,0:15:52.74,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Or perhaps, indulge your curiosity\Nand become a professional writer.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.74,0:15:56.31,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No, maybe just a novelist who aims for a niche market.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.31,0:15:59.54,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Since you like computers, I guess art design might work.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.54,0:16:03.42,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Maybe a scenario writer who uses\Nrandom material instead of an actual story writer.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.42,0:16:04.58,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Or she doesn't go to college...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.09,0:16:07.17,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Or they're all the same thing?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.17,0:16:08.09,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.22,0:16:12.59,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.18,0:16:14.22,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Manager!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.22,0:16:15.93,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Legendary Girl A...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.93,0:16:17.16,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...has returned!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.14,0:16:19.81,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.35,0:16:22.52,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,She shook us off last time!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.52,0:16:23.08,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(575,457)}Manager!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.08,0:16:23.58,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(117,459)}Manager!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.58,0:16:24.06,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(242,459)}Manager!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.06,0:16:25.81,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Today!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.73,0:16:32.11,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We will absolutely make sure she\Nreaches the goal known as our register!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.40,0:16:32.82,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Giro.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.32,0:16:35.03,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,She seems to be at a loss.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.87,0:16:37.03,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Then allow us to...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.03,0:16:39.03,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...help her find her way!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.95,0:16:40.74,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.75,0:16:41.54,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Let 'er rip!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.54,0:16:41.98,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.98,0:16:42.69,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.69,0:16:42.98,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.98,0:16:43.64,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.64,0:16:44.02,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.02,0:16:44.85,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.85,0:16:45.81,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Aw yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.29,0:16:49.13,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Manager.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.13,0:16:52.17,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Attempting to determine Legendary Girl A's objective for the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.72,0:16:53.17,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.17,0:16:53.55,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Countin' on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.13,0:16:55.34,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the newest comic out?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.34,0:16:56.09,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.09,0:16:57.30,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Volume 14 of Sgt. Frog, sah!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.64,0:16:58.18,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.16,0:16:59.89,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Raise the height of our goods to the appropriate level...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.89,0:17:01.89,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...to bring them to the attention of Legendary Girl A!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.33,0:17:02.08,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.89,0:17:03.52,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And deploy the flyers!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.52,0:17:04.25,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Tama!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.31,0:17:06.40,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Deployment complete!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.40,0:17:07.10,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Sah!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.65,0:17:08.48,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.48,0:17:10.07,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep an eye on her movements.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.57,0:17:13.11,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And as Legendary Girl A approaches the register...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.11,0:17:15.07,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...deploy our best-selling goods!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.07,0:17:16.03,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.03,0:17:16.78,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Sah!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.12,0:17:19.45,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.58,0:17:21.41,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Manager!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.41,0:17:24.87,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Legendary Girl A's objective isn't the comics section!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.87,0:17:25.79,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.00,0:17:27.71,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Manager.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.71,0:17:29.96,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Switch target to the DVD section.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.09,0:17:30.84,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.84,0:17:32.21,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Just to be sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.21,0:17:35.49,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...block all side paths so Legendary Girl A...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.49,0:17:36.84,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...heads straight to the new DVD section!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.84,0:17:37.72,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.72,0:17:38.26,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Sah!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.01,0:17:40.64,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.89,0:17:42.51,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Tama! Tama!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.06,0:17:43.97,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.98,0:17:45.85,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Forgive me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.85,0:17:48.02,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}Gero-gero-gero-gero build-up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.85,0:17:48.02,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}Tama-tama-tama-tama build-up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.00,0:17:51.71,ls_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(79,233)}New
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.56,0:17:51.07,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.32,0:17:59.03,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Manager!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.03,0:18:00.91,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,She's...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.12,0:18:03.79,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...picked up the item!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.79,0:18:06.91,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I've finally become a winner today!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.92,0:18:07.67,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Comrades!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.67,0:18:10.04,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Let us have a wild celebration tonight!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.04,0:18:10.54,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.54,0:18:11.46,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Sah!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.75,0:18:14.25,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a feint!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.03,0:18:20.03,ls_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(51,66)\frz17.185\frx356\fry16}Ridiculously Cheap!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.68,0:18:24.97,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have to bring out my trump card!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.40,0:18:30.10,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Come...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.11,0:18:34.19,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Bring that bargain, super-rare, out-of-print DVD to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.53,0:18:37.28,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Manager.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.28,0:18:38.36,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,She is heading for the register.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.70,0:18:39.45,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.45,0:18:40.61,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep going!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.53,0:18:44.12,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What a beautiful scene!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.12,0:18:46.87,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The crowd inside me is cheering with applause right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.87,0:18:47.71,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.71,0:18:48.21,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Sah!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.21,0:18:51.21,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Your total comes to 1,785 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.60,0:19:03.76,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm short 3 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.43,0:19:07.18,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.18,0:19:09.23,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Please put that back.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.11,0:19:16.19,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be back!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.07,0:19:23.49,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Good lucky!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.49,0:19:24.16,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.16,0:19:26.04,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's kick this into gear!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.04,0:19:30.08,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We're already on the thirteenth episode of Lucky Channel!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.08,0:19:30.54,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.54,0:19:33.75,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,As you already know, I'm your navigator, Akira Kogami!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.75,0:19:35.09,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.09,0:19:35.54,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.48,0:19:37.36,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}D-D-Drill!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.61,0:19:39.28,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}D-D-Drill!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.55,0:19:37.67,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Akira-sama's assistant, Minoru Shiraishi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.67,0:19:39.47,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a pleasure!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.47,0:19:40.76,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.61,0:19:41.32,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}D-D-Drill!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.66,0:19:43.41,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}D-D-D-D-Drill!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.76,0:19:41.97,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We're on episode 13.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.97,0:19:43.97,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Into the second season.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.57,0:19:45.16,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}D-D-Drill!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.45,0:19:46.99,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}D-D-Drill!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.33,0:19:48.91,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}D-D-D-D-Drill!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.97,0:19:49.56,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like we've reached the fifth station on Mt. Fuji, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.56,0:19:50.39,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Mt. Fuji?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.39,0:19:52.60,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You can drive up to the fifth station.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.73,0:19:55.52,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's true...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.52,0:19:56.19,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.19,0:19:58.32,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I've climbed Mt. Takao before!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.99,0:20:00.99,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you have something else to talk about?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.99,0:20:02.45,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's true...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.99,0:20:03.47,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}D-D-D-D-D-D-D-D-Drill!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.45,0:20:04.07,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.07,0:20:06.20,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Akira-sama's twin drills look wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.20,0:20:07.99,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What's so wonderful about them?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.83,0:20:10.66,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The way they go round and round like a shell.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.50,0:20:13.21,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.71,0:20:14.83,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.83,0:20:16.21,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We have a special announcement today.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.80,0:20:19.76,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The results for the Lucky Star figure poll!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.76,0:20:22.55,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's have Akira-sama announce the results!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.30,0:20:27.16,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The characters that will soon be getting figures are Konata Izumi...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.03,0:20:37.42,ls_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(319,482)}Current Standings 1st: Minoru Shiraishi 2nd: Akira Kogami 3rd: Kagami Hiiragi 4th: Konata Izumi 5th: Tsukasa Hiiragi 6th: Minami Iwasaki 7th: Misao Kusakabe 8th: Miyuki Takara 9th: Kanata Izumi 10th: Yutaka Kobayakawa {scrolls at the bottom}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.10,0:20:27.18,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Akira-sama, do a proper job!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.18,0:20:28.83,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Congratulations!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.83,0:20:30.50,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh, everybody knew this would happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.50,0:20:32.58,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What a joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.58,0:20:34.58,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}No, no, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.27,0:20:38.02,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Just means that the higher-ups think the\Nactual show is more important than this corner.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.02,0:20:39.94,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course not, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.55,0:20:51.73,ls_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(319,482)}Current Standings 1st: Minoru Shiraishi 2nd: Akira Kogami 3rd: Kagami Hiiragi 4th: Konata Izumi 5th: Tsukasa Hiiragi 6th: Minami Iwasaki 7th: Misao Kusakabe 8th: Miyuki Takara 9th: Kanata Izumi 10th: Yutaka Kobayakawa {scrolls at the bottom}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.26,0:20:42.80,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.80,0:20:44.59,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The producers agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.59,0:20:45.72,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.72,0:20:47.51,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll just fall for your little trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.51,0:20:49.62,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm already used to being backstabbed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.62,0:20:51.04,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Little trick?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.04,0:20:52.91,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's an awful thing to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.91,0:20:57.92,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And don't tell me that it says you're going to have a figure made.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.94,0:21:07.12,ls_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(319,482)}Current Standings 1st: Minoru Shiraishi 2nd: Akira Kogami 3rd: Kagami Hiiragi 4th: Konata Izumi 5th: Tsukasa Hiiragi 6th: Minami Iwasaki 7th: Misao Kusakabe 8th: Miyuki Takara 9th: Kanata Izumi 10th: Yutaka Kobayakawa {scrolls at the bottom}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.57,0:20:59.48,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course not!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.48,0:20:59.86,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.86,0:21:02.42,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be making a figure of Konata Izumi-san this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.42,0:21:05.63,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And the popular Minoru Shiraishi will also get a figure?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.61,0:21:07.18,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The hell is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.18,0:21:08.68,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,U-Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.39,0:21:11.56,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's time to say goodbye!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.56,0:21:16.98,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So please send us any suggestions or comments you have!
